snippet.title: Ray Comfort: 'Noah' Movie Disrespectful, Not Biblically Accurate

localized.description:
--Ray Comfort, co-host of the TV program The Way Of The Master joins David to discuss his displeasure with the Hollywood movie Noah and another version of the movie that he is producing

--On the Bonus Show: Sbarro files chapter 11...again, California moves to ban killer whale shows, Louis' experience with SXSW, more...
